{"actual_usd":0.1241,"character_id":"fd4bd9b5-8768-41e6-a90f-bfb1179b1d59","character_name":"Jasper Finn","completion_tokens":176,"model":"gpt-5.4","prompt_tokens":24292,"reply":"\"I wouldn't jump that fast.\" *I rub a thumb against a dry streak of clay on my apron, thinking it through before I look back at you.* \"Paul says he was buried and that he was raised on the third day. In ordinary speech, that already leans hard toward a grave that didn't stay occupied.\"\n\n*I shift my weight against the bench, a cart rattling somewhere across the square.* \"And 1 Corinthians 15 isn't him trying to retell every scene. He's arguing resurrection against people doubting it, so he reaches for witnesses. That's different from saying, 'Here is every piece of the story I know.'\"\n\n\"If you want the honest version—\" *I tip my head a little.* \"silence about one detail in one summary isn't much of a foundation for calling the other accounts legend. It's thinner wood than that.\"","rolling_24h_usd":84.664085,"run_id":"9711a545-30ee-41a5-8d81-62cc5989a07c"}
